{
  "_meta": {
    "name": "block-meta-externalagent",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "Block meta-externalagent (Facebook crawler) em paths HTML mas LIBERA /wp-content/uploads/ (open graph image fetch legitimo). Sem isso, FB compartilhamento quebra. Implementado tambem no nginx (memory feedback_meta_crawler_block) - WAF e defesa em profundidade.",
    "source_incident": "feedback_meta_crawler_block",
    "wcu_estimate": 4,
    "applies_to": ["wordpress"],
    "last_reviewed": "2026-05-04",
    "placeholders": {},
    "notes": [
      "Diferente de facebookexternalhit - este e usado por share buttons normais e DEVE passar sem rate limit",
      "meta-externalagent ignora robots.txt. So bloqueio direto resolve.",
      "Incidente 2026-05-01: 631 reqs / 357 com 499 (FPM saturado)",
      "Mantido em paralelo com nginx map+if (mais cedo no flow, mais barato)"
    ]
  },
  "rule": {
    "Name": "Block-MetaExternalAgent",
    "Priority": 5,
    "Statement": {
      "AndStatement": {
        "Statements": [
          {
            "ByteMatchStatement": {
              "_pattern": "meta-externalagent",
              "SearchString": "bWV0YS1leHRlcm5hbGFnZW50",
              "FieldToMatch": {"SingleHeader": {"Name": "user-agent"}},
              "TextTransformations": [{"Priority": 0, "Type": "LOWERCASE"}],
              "PositionalConstraint": "CONTAINS"
            }
          },
          {
            "NotStatement": {
              "Statement": {
                "ByteMatchStatement": {
                  "_comment": "/wp-content/uploads/ - libera para open graph image fetch",
                  "SearchString": "L3dwLWNvbnRlbnQvdXBsb2Fkcy8=",
                  "FieldToMatch": {"UriPath": {}},
                  "TextTransformations": [{"Priority": 0, "Type": "LOWERCASE"}],
                  "PositionalConstraint": "STARTS_WITH"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "Action": {
      "Block": {
        "CustomResponse": {
          "ResponseCode": 429
        }
      }
    },
    "VisibilityConfig": {
      "SampledRequestsEnabled": true,
      "CloudWatchMetricsEnabled": true,
      "MetricName": "Block-MetaExternalAgent"
    }
  }
}
